sign-470x284.png 470w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/brandmark-design.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n			<h2>Vision</h2>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n										Connect through passions\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Democratize Workplace Interactions using rank-blind matching\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Create fun, natural work environment for those at home \n									</li>\n						</ul>\n			<h2>Mission</h2>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n										Provide supplementary software to enhance Microsoft Teams experience\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Give entry-level employees the opportunity to chat with a CEO, COO, or any executive about passions they share\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Let people look forward to remote-work\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n			<h2>Values</h2>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n										Seamless user experiences\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Enhancing productivity in large and small firms\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Strength among teams, groups within larger organizations \n									</li>\n						</ul>\n			<h2>Team</h2>		\n		<p>Meet our team</p>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1072-1-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1072-1-300x300.png 300w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1072-1-100x100.png 100w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1072-1-470x470.png 470w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1072-1-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1072-1-150x150.png 150w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1072-1-768x768.png 768w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG_1072-1.png 1122w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n		<p>Devin Pracar</p><p>Founder</p><p>Devin Pracar is 20 years old, and one of the youngest CEOs in the media business. Startup entrepreneur and competitive skier, Devin is passionate about politics, philosophy, and social dynamics. Devin was studying at Cal when college students across the world were affected by Covid-19. He started a media business in Oregon during the pandemic, and knows firsthand the needs of people struggling with remote-learning and working environments.</p><center> <a href=\"mailto:devin@watercooler.fun\">devin@watercooler.fun</a></center>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2-ConvertImage-1-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2-ConvertImage-1-300x300.png 300w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2-ConvertImage-1-100x100.png 100w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2-ConvertImage-1-470x470.png 470w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2-ConvertImage-1-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2-ConvertImage-1-150x150.png 150w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2-ConvertImage-1-768x768.png 768w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2-ConvertImage-1-1536x1536.png 1536w, https://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2-ConvertImage-1-2048x2048.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n		<p>Liam Cisneros Morley</p><p>Founder</p><p>Liam Cisneros Morley studied Math and Economics at The University of Southern California. Born and raised in the San Francisco Bay Area, Liam is passionate about building strong human connections, and using new methods and technologies to strengthen and grow our human potential.</p><center> <a href=\"mailto:liam@watercooler.fun\">liam@watercooler.fun</a></center>		\n										<img src=\"http://watercoolerusa.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/cameron-scaled-p50fmf0xhbnqx1m4fhedn5p9in5k0xw0w8wiu0bsqg.jpeg\" title=\"cameron\" alt=\"cameron\" />											\n		<p>Cameron Bolt</p><p>Founder</p>Cameron Bolt is one of the founders at Watercooler, working on the development and construction of the Watercooler bot. He is currently studying Economics and Political Science at Yale University. Cameron is especially interested in Finance, political theory, and technology. Cameron values collaboration and determination and had found those to be immensely useful in the development of Watercooler with the rest of the Watercooler team\n<center> <a href=\"mailto:cameron@watercooler.fun\">cameron@watercooler.fun</a></center>','About','\n						','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2021-04-01 12:06:04','2021-04-01 12:06:04','',0,'http://8560c281.ngrok.io/?page_id=116',0,'page','',0),(1186,1,'2019-03-01 10:03:40','2019-03-01 10:03:40','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit.<br>\nArchitecto atque aut blanditiis consectetur</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Albums','\n						','publish','closed','closed','','albums','','','2019-03-01 10:03:40','2019-03-01 10:03:40','',0,'http://8560c281.ngrok.io/?page_id=149',0,'page','',0),(1187,1,'2019-03-01 10:08:18','2019-03-01 10:08:18','<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit.<br />Architecto atque aut blanditiis consectetur</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','Artists','\n						','publish','closed','closed','','artists','','','2019-03-01 10:08:18','2019-03-01 10:08:18','',0,'http://8560c281.ngrok.io/?page_id=153',0,'page','',0),(1190,1,'2019-03-06 08:27:43','2019-03-06 08:27:43','<section data-bg-possition=\"